      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to amend title 38, United States code, to provide for the payment of a monthly stipend to the surviving parents (known as "Gold Star Parents") of members of the Armed Forces who die during a period of war.</title>
